<h1>{{title}}</h1>

<div id="travel-flex">
    <div id="travel-text">
        <h2 id="travel-text-title">Indian Sub-Continent</h2>
        <p>While I have travelled to many different countries, one of the most
            amazing trips was an around-the-world trip that included four months
            in the Indian sub-continent.</p>
        <p>In the following photos, you will see the following:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>A camel safari trip I took in the deserts of Rajasthan,
                India</li>
            <li>Two residents I spent the day with in the desert.</li>
            <li>The border crossing on the Karakoram Highway between India and
                Pakistan.</li>
        </ul>
        <div id="travel-country-image">
            <img src="/images/travel/india_flag.png" style="width:50%">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="travel-photos">
        <div class="travel-slideshow fade">
            <img id="panama" src="/images/travel/india1.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="travel-slideshow fade">
            <img id="kara" src="/images/travel/india2.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="travel-slideshow fade">
            <img id="india" src="/images/travel/india3.jpg"
                style="width:100%">
        </div>

        <a id="previous" onclick="nextSlide(-1)">❮</a>
        <a id="next" onclick="nextSlide(1)">❯</a>

        <div style="text-align:center">
            <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(1)"></span>
            <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(2)"></span>
            <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(3)"></span>
        </div>

    </div>
